sources.title: Final Days Of Planet Earth | Part 2 of 2 | FULL MOVIE | Action, Thriller
sources.description:
When the tragic team of astronauts enlisted to excavate the moon returns to earth, it brings with it an alien-insect race that must harvest human bodies for survival. As their underground colony thrives, so does the fear that mankind’s end has arrived.

Watch part 1 here if you missed it! https://youtu.be/tJMwwnJmioc

Daryl Hannah
Campbell Scott
Gil Bellows
Suleka Mathew
Serge Houde
Beau Starr
Patrick Gilmore

2006
Directed by Robert Lieberman
